{"parse":{"title":"Bloated Giant Sunfish","pageid":157443,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|name=Bloated Giant Sunfish\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_03\n|quality=common\n|effect=&lt;Right Click to Open&gt;\n|ilvl=70\n|sell={{cost|s=1}}\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\nThe '''Bloated Giant Sunfish''' is a special {{item|Giant Sunfish}}.\n\n==Source==\nThe Fish may be caught in the water surrounding the [[Sunwell Isle]].\n\n==Possible contents==\n*{{item|icon=|Darkclaw Lobster}}\n*{{item|icon=|Stranglekelp}}\n*{{item|icon=|Netherbloom}}\n*{{item|icon=|Mana Thistle}}\n*{{item|icon=|Scroll of Protection V}}\n*{{item|icon=|Scroll of Agility V}}\n*{{item|icon=|Adamantite Ore}}\n*{{item|icon=|Nightmare Vine}}\n*{{item|icon=|Terocone}}\n*{{item|icon=|Seaweed}}\n\n== Patch changes ==\n{{Patch 2.4.0|note=Added}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|35286}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/bloated_giant_sunfish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft container items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]"}}}